課程概述 Course Description
       討論 interpolation及polynomial approximation,線性代數,非線性代數,常微分方程, 常微分方程組,偏微分方程,矩陣的特徵值與特徵向量及有限元素法之解決技巧及誤差The course presents numerical schemes and discussion for solving mathematical problems: solutions for one-variable equations, Lagrange’s interpolation, Hermite’s interpolation, integral method including Gaussian Quadrature, linear algebra including the eigen-value problems, initial-value problems, boundary-value problems including the Rayleigh-Ritz method, least square approximation including FFT , solutions for nonlinear systems of equations, partial differential equations and finite-element technique.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
教導如何把已知的數學問題如何轉化成數值計算並應用計算機於執行任務。 讓學生建立更有效率及更精準之工程分析執行方法。訓練學生獨立思考與研究的能力。 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Mathematical Preliminaries, solutions of Equations in one variables2Mathematical Preliminaries, solutions of Equations in one variables3Interpolation and polynomial approximation, numerical differential and integration4Interpolation and polynomial approximation, numerical differential and integration5Initial value problem for ordinary differential equation6Initial value problem for ordinary differential equation7Solving linear systems8Solving linear systems9第一次考試10Approximation theory, eigenvalues and eigenvectors11Approximation theory, eigenvalues and eigenvectors12Systems of nonlinear equations13Systems of nonlinear equations14Boundary value problem for ordinary differential equation15Partial differential equations and finite element method.16Partial differential equations and finite element method.17Partial differential equations and finite element method.18NA 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


